description:
This headphone stand is made to hold your professional headphone and at the same display it on any surface. It can hold two headphones at the same timeThe stand will keep your headphone from resting on a desk collecting dust inside the earcups and the headphone itself get scratches overtime. From laying on a table but hang it. This stand protects the left and right earcups from dusts entering when not using.
